(I'm going to keep Unitron and Firestarter in seperate posts from my larger 
guys so that my big war post isn't too large)

Unitron/Firestarter:



Unitron saw the lockdown take effect and cursed, as all his and Firestarter's 
work was for nothing.  "By the Void!"

---

"Calm down." Firestarter replied to his ranting.  "Everything will be 
complete in due time." he said, raising an arm and firing off a missile at 
the hatch.

Unitron sighed pointing his head at the door, his two inwardly pointing horns 
firing out, drilling into the door.  He stood up, the horns still drilling 
into the side, now unreachable from the outside world.

"They shall drill until they are int he very center of the hatch. Then they 
shall explode with the force of several charges."

"See, I told you not to worry." Firestarter fired, raising his other arm and 
firing off a missile into the access hatch.
